1.5px;\">2</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space: normal; border: 1px solid #000000; width: 161.5px;\">1</td><td style=\"white-space: normal; border: 1px solid #000000; width: 161.5px;\">1</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space: normal; border: 1px solid #000000; width: 161.5px;\">1</td><td style=\"white-space: normal; border: 1px solid #000000; width: 161.5px;\">1</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space: normal; border: 1px solid #000000; width: 161.5px;\">1</td><td style=\"white-space: normal; border: 1px solid #000000; width: 161.5px;\">1</td></tr></tbody></table><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;&#x00BB;</p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><i>b)</i> L&#x2019;avant dernier alin&#x00E9;a est ainsi modifi&#x00E9;&nbsp;:</p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&#x2013;&nbsp;les mots&nbsp;: &#x00AB;&nbsp;dans le&nbsp;&#x00BB; sont remplac&#x00E9;s par les mots&nbsp;: &#x00AB;&nbsp;&#x00E0; la septi&#x00E8;me et &#x00E0; la huiti&#x00E8;me ligne du&nbsp;&#x00BB;&nbsp;;&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&#x2013;&nbsp;le taux&nbsp;: &#x00AB;&nbsp;5&nbsp;%&nbsp;&#x00BB; est remplac&#x00E9; par le taux&nbsp;: &#x00AB;&nbsp;7&nbsp;%&nbsp;&#x00BB;&nbsp;;</p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&#x2013;&nbsp;la seconde occurrence du mot&nbsp;: &#x00AB;&nbsp;tarif&nbsp;&#x00BB; est remplac&#x00E9;e par le mot&nbsp;: &#x00AB;&nbsp;taux&nbsp;&#x00BB;.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">2&#x00B0;&nbsp;Les deuxi&#x00E8;me et derni&#x00E8;re colonnes du tableau du&nbsp;troisi&#x00E8;me alin&#x00E9;a du&nbsp;I de l&#x2019;article&nbsp;L.&nbsp;2333&#x2011;41 sont ainsi r&#x00E9;dig&#x00E9;es&nbsp;:</p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&#x00AB;&nbsp;</p><table style=\"border-collapse: collapse; height: 159px;\" width=\"402\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"white-space: normal; border: 1px solid #000000; width: 197.5px;\">Tarif plancher (en euros)&nbsp;</td><td style=\"white-space: normal; border: 1px solid #000000; width: 197.5px;\">Tarif plafond (en euros)</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space: normal; border: 1px solid #000000; width: 197.5px;\">2,5</td><td style=\"white-space: normal; border: 1px solid #000000; width: 197.5px;\">10</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space: normal; border: 1px solid #000000; width: 197.5px;\">2</td><td style=\"white-space: normal; border: 1px solid #000000; width: 197.5px;\">10</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space: normal; border: 1px solid #000000; width: 197.5px;\">1</td><td style=\"white-space: normal; border: 1px solid #000000; width: 197.5px;\">4</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space: normal; border: 1px solid #000000; width: 197.5px;\">0,5</td><td style=\"white-space: normal; border: 1px solid #000000; width: 197.5px;\">1,5</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space: normal; border: 1px solid #000000; width: 197.5px;\">0,3</td><td style=\"white-space: normal; border: 1px solid #000000; width: 197.5px;\">0,9</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space: normal; border: 1px solid #000000; width: 197.5px;\">0,2</td><td style=\"white-space: normal; border: 1px solid #000000; width: 197.5px;\">0,8</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space: normal; border: 1px solid #000000; width: 197.5px;\">0,2</td><td style=\"white-space: normal; border: 1px solid #000000; width: 197.5px;\">0,6</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space: normal; border: 1px solid #000000; width: 197.5px;\">0,2</td><td style=\"white-space: normal; border: 1px solid #000000; width: 197.5px;\">0,2</td></tr></tbody></table>", "avantAppel": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "exposeSommaire": "<p>Le pr&#x00E9;sent amendement introduit une modification &#x00E0; l&#x2019;&#x00E9;chelle des tarifs fixes par cat&#x00E9;gorie d&#x2019;h&#x00E9;bergement, en permettant aux collectivit&#x00E9;s territoriales de d&#x00E9;finir des proportionnels au prix de la nuit&#x00E9;e sur le mod&#x00E8;le de ce qui existe d&#x00E9;j&#x00E0; pour les meubl&#x00E9;s de tourisme.</p><p>Ce taux proportionnel s&#x2019;appliquera &#x00E0; tous les h&#x00E9;bergements, qu&#x2019;ils soient class&#x00E9;s, en attente de classement ou sans classement. Il est n&#x00E9;anmoins propos&#x00E9; de moduler ce taux proportionnel en fonction de la cat&#x00E9;gorie d&#x2019;h&#x00E9;bergement afin de moduler le tarif de la taxe de s&#x00E9;jour en fonction du prestige des h&#x00E9;bergements.</p>", "annexeExposeSommaire": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}}}, "cycleDeVie": {"dateDepot": "2025-10-22", "datePublication": "2025-10-26", "soumisArticle40": "true", "etatDesTraitements": {"etat": {"code": "AC", "libelle": "A discuter"}, "sousEtat": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}}, "dateSort": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "sort": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}}, "representations": {"representation": {"nom": "PDF", "typeMime": {"type": "application", "subType": "PDF"}, "statutRepresentation": {"verbatim": "true", "canonique": "true", "officielle": "true", "transcription": "false", "enregistrement": "false"}, "repSource": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "offset": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "contenu": {"documentURI": "/base/AMANR5L17PO838901B1906P1D1N003412?format=pdf"}, "dateDispoRepresentation": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}}}, "seanceDiscussionRef": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "article99": "false", "loiReference": {"codeLoi": "CGCT", "divisionCodeLoi": "L2333-30"}, "discussionCommune": {"idDiscussion": "34943", "typePosition": "Milieu"}, "discussionIdentique": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "accordGouvernementDepotHorsDelai": "Sans objet"}}